<TITLE> Police nab DU student possessing gun </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Apr 19 (bdnews24.com)Police on Monday detained Dhaka University student Mohammad Arif in possession of a revolver. Arif is an activist of Surja Sen Hall Unit of Chhatra League and a final year student of history. Md Rakibul Islam, duty officer of the Kotwali Police Station, told bdnews24.com that Arif was arrested at Babubazar check-post while he was coming from Keraniganj on a motorcycle. Police stopped him for routine inspection and found a revolver in his waist. His motorcycle and two mobile phones were seized. A case against him was underway, the police official said. b
